The '''Information Centre on Academic Mobility and Equivalence''' (CIMEA) is the Italian centre in the [[National Academic Recognition Information Centre]] (NARIC) network.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.enic-naric.net/index.aspx?c=Italy |title=Italy |publisher=ENIC-NARIC.net}}</ref> It was established in 1984 and since 1986 has operated through an agreement with [[Italy]]'s [[Ministry of Education, Universities and Research (Italy)|Ministry of Education, Universities and Research]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cimea.it/default.aspx?IDC=18 |title=Mission |work=CIMEA website}}</ref>
